coverageContract.note: Unstable namespaces are sourced from all unstable index barrels, then marked if explicitly listed in package exports.

rules: Each public module import path has exactly one primary skill owner.
Primary skills may only cover one module import path.
Facet skills may only subdivide one parent module and must link back to that parent.
Router skills provide navigation only and own no module behavior.
Every skill includes Owned scope, Not covered here, and Escalate to sections.
